  "texts": [
    "To address this, we focus on a more lightweight and adaptable approach to user history selection.",
    "Since our approach relies on embedding editing to adapt the model, we need to identify userrepresentative historical data.",
    "The first step is to define what makes this data \"representative.\"",
    "We leverage sentence embeddings for their strong ability to capture both the meaning and context of text (Reimers and Gurevych, 2019).",
    "Our goal is to find the most informative and relevant embedding pieces that reflect key user preferences."
  ],
